Package: biostrext
Type: Package
Title: Extension to Biostrings
Version: 0.1.0
Author: Pawel Krawczyk
Maintainer: Pawel Krawczyk <p.krawczyk@ibb.waw.pl>
Description: Extends Biostrings functionality
    Provide convenient functions for %GC calculation, splitting of DNA sequence with sliding window
    and calculation of %GC on generated fragments. Generate plots of %GC across sequence.
